            <h2>Job Offerings</h2>
            <h3>Full-Time Positions</h3>
            <p>PwC offers various full-time job opportunities across different domains, including audit, consulting, tax, and advisory services. Salaries for full-time positions are competitive and based on experience and qualifications.</p>
            <h3>Part-Time Positions</h3>
            <p>Part-time employment opportunities are available in areas such as administrative support, data analysis, and research. Part-time employees receive competitive hourly wages.</p>
            <h3>Work from Home</h3>
            <p>PwC provides remote work opportunities in fields such as technology, digital marketing, and project management. Work-from-home positions offer flexibility and competitive compensation packages.</p>
            <h3>Internships with Stipend</h3>
            <p>PwC offers internship programs for undergraduate and graduate students seeking practical experience in accounting, consulting, and other business areas. Interns receive stipends, and the amount varies depending on factors such as location and duration.</p>
